- feature_033: slope -8.604e-4, p=6.04e-6.
- feature_032: response-rate difference -0.024217, p=3.23e-5.

Independent effects after adjustment for all feature columns:
- feature_027: adjusted coefficient -0.052254, p=<1e-300.
- feature_015: adjusted coefficient 0.056298, p=<1e-300.
- feature_025: adjusted coefficient 0.067366, p=<1e-300.
- feature_031: adjusted coefficient -7.701e-4, p=<1e-300.
